This key/value mapping is used for building the query parameters._It is expected to be of the generic type java.util.Map where the keys are the named parameters_of a given JPA query and the values are their corresponding effective values you want to select for.

_

When it's used for producer, Simple expression can be used as a parameter value. It allows you to_retrieve parameter values from the message body, header and etc.
